# ── Monorepo root ignore (Solo-OS) ──
# Applies across both Website/ and Mobile app/. Nested .gitignore files still apply too.

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Env / secrets — NEVER commit real values
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Python venv (mobile tooling)
**/.venv/

# Next.js (website)
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/.vercel/
**/next-env.d.ts
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Expo / React Native (mobile)
**/.expo/
**/dist/
**/web-build/
**/expo-env.d.ts
**/.metro-health-check*

# Native signing material
**/*.jks
**/*.p8
**/*.p12
**/*.key
**/*.mobileprovision
**/credentials.json

# Local Prisma DB files
**/prisma/*.db
**/prisma/*.db-journal

# Supabase local
**/supabase/.temp/
**/supabase/.branches/

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.*
**/yarn-debug.*
**/yarn-error.*

# Scratch / temp
**/.tmp_*
**/*.orig.*

# OS / IDE
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
*.iml
